<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<topic id="both-now">

    <title>
     <section xml:lang="en">Both now:</section>
     <section xml:lang="ar" dir="rtl">الآنَ</section>
     <section xml:lang="el">Καὶ νῦν:</section>
     <section xml:lang="cu">И ны́нѣ:</section>
     <section xml:lang="ru">И ныне:</section>
    </title>
 
    <shortdesc>Both now:</shortdesc>
 
    <body>
 
     <section xml:lang="en">
          <p>Both now and ever, and unto ages of ages. Amen.</p>
     </section>
     <section xml:lang="ar" dir="rtl">
           <p>.الآنَ وكُلَّ أوانٍ وإلى دَهْرِ الداهِرين. آمين</p>
     </section>
     <section xml:lang="el">
           <p>Καὶ νῦν, καὶ ἀεί, καὶ εἰς τοὺς αἰῶνας τῶν αἰώνων. Ἀμήν.</p>
     </section>
     <section xml:lang="cu">
          <p>И ны́нѣ и҆ при́снѡ, и҆ во вѣ́ки вѣкѡ́въ. А҆ми́нь.</p>
     </section>
     <section xml:lang="ru">
           <p>И ныне и присно и во веки веков. Аминь.</p>
     </section>
 
    </body>
 
 </topic>